.livesdk__proactiveMsg { box-sizing: content-box; padding: 24px 5px; display: flex; pointer-events: none; max-width: 320px; overflow: hidden; width: max-content; position: absolute; right: 0px; flex-direction: column; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; row-gap: 16px; }

.livesdk__proactiveMsg__message { border-radius: 5px; width: 100%; opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); transition: 0.2s ease-in-out; align-self: flex-start; animation-fill-mode: forwards; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-end; }

.livesdk__proactiveMsg__message__closeIcon { pointer-events: auto; display: flex; width: 24px; height: 24px; padding: 5px; position: relative; right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; justify-content: center; align-items: center; flex-shrink: 0; box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 24px; border: 1px solid rgb(223, 227, 232); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-shadow: rgba(19, 22, 25, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px, rgba(19, 22, 25, 0.1) 0px 2px 4px; backdrop-filter: blur(5px); cursor: pointer; transition: 0.1s; }

.livesdk__proactiveMsg__message__bubble { pointer-events: auto; display: inline-flex; padding: 10px 12px; justify-content: flex-end; align-items: center; gap: 8px; max-width: 320px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid rgb(223, 227, 232); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 48); transition: 0.11s ease-in; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08) 0px 2px 4px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08) 0px 4px 8px; }
.livesdk__proactiveMsg__message__buttons { width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px; }

.livesdk__proactiveMsg__message__buttons-btn { display: inline-flex; padding: 10px 12px; align-items: center; gap: 8px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgb(14, 114, 237); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08) 0px 2px 4px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08) 0px 4px 8px; color: rgb(14, 114, 237); text-align: center; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; cursor: pointer; }
